data.actual_result: You return to general account settings which is not part of the call settings / dm call.
data.expected_result: To return to the call from voice settings directly
data.short_description: When you access voice settings from a call, then click the back button to return to the call you return to general account settings instead of returning to the call
data.steps_to_repro: - Get in a DM call - Click the three dots - Click voice settings  - Press back in the top left hand corner  - Observe that it takes you to general account settings
